  "title": "Technical Engineer",
  "description": "<ul><li>Overseeing projects at one or multiple stipulated sites.</li><li>Assist project manager is the execution of the projects.</li><li>Responsibilites for co-ordination with Consultants, Architects and relevant authorities.</li><li>Liaise with Consultants, Main contractor, Suppliers, Sub contractor on Equipment & Material submissions.</li><li>Monitor and ensure progress of works are carried out according to project specification.</li><li>Assist drafting team for design schematic drawing, layout drawing, P&ID drawing.</li><li>Review and check drawing before submit to main contractor.</li><li>Oversee the overall planning of ACMV works, site inspection, variation order and certification of work done for all assigned projects.</li><li>Support project manager in the administration of contract, claim, variation and any dispute arise.</li><li>Raise MR and order material & arrange manpower for necessary works.</li><li>Advise site team for work schedule and technical issues.</li><li>Make sure project is carried out according to schedule.</li><li>Responsible for site supervision and implementation.</li><li>Responsible for ensuring implementing safety measures</li></ul>",
